Package: tisch
Title: Another Table Generator for LaTeX Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christian", "Rubba", email = "r@christianrubba.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The tisch package provides a way for generating LaTeX tables with
    intrica. It can documents. It provides a formula interface based on reshape2's
    casting function and allows users to assign variables to columns and rows. tisch
    assand the arrangement of cell values. A theming system gives easy control over
    aesthetic aspects of the tables.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    reshape2,
    infuser,
    methods,
    tools,
    stringr
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr
